      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        Traumatic brain injury (PMSI code (Programme Médicalisation des Systèmes d'Information) S
        06.70 and S 06.71) Age&gt;14 years Surviving more than 6h after the trauma Hospitalized in the
        traumatic brain injury intensive care unit and managed in accordance with international
        guidelines Who underwent a cerebral CT-scan

        Exclusion Criteria:

        Ongoing treatment with anticoagulants or antiplatelets Pregnant women Persons without
        national health insurance cover Children less than 15 years old Under guardianship.
      </textblock>
